@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yunojg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.27 + ((v1 + 0.02 + v2 + 0.71) + wp.abs(v0 + 0.01)))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin((tmp + 0.10 / v1 + 0.99)))
    data[tid] = v0
